{"tid":2072032,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲英譯中嘅人名咁正，點解喺本地人裏面又咁少見？","createTime":"2020-06-20T09:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:55:07.000Z","uid":213357,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c30aadcfc06e940f95a7d48832e2533296833ae","tid":2072032,"uid":213357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"就好似，美國總統：亞伯拉罕&middot;<span style=\"color: red;\">林肯</span>，哲學家：伯蘭特&middot;<span style=\"color: red;\">羅素</span>，圓桌騎士：<span style=\"color: red;\">高文</span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔理佢真實存在或者係虛構人物。林，羅，高，都係華人世界常見嘅姓。但本地就好少見到啲好似林肯呢類型咁正嘅名，可能係我見識少。又或者佢哋太出名，聽得多就覺得好聽。<br />\n<br />\n近代嚟講我聽過比較出名又好聽嘅：葉問<br />\n<br />\n三國嗰啲又型又好聽：呂布，曹操，但太耐了，大家有冇聽過啲咩靚名？要近代啲嘅。"},{"pid":"f12f83f90065a3acf665ca0fa5f5bb344e9abd4c","tid":2072032,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"羅利控"},{"pid":"fcc327adb7717887bcd0373e855577dd9ea2ee0b","tid":2072032,"uid":348813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"羅宋湯"},{"pid":"1a4e5ab231e8f90366c7b89b24f5db9b4ab385c5","tid":2072032,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"林正式 羅正式"},{"pid":"beb4a5dfba37db9ee745c69a0ae3e935c224a899","tid":2072032,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"段崇智"},{"pid":"d6e0d827ce2490fb01f97528360d330801e8b2e3","tid":2072032,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"令計劃<br />\n令完成"},{"pid":"dfea2ee8bb996521147ccb8ffdfa88a070be76b4","tid":2072032,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"都有嘅，林敏聰將自己個仔改名做林肯"}]}